Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone through every\Nbook in Ponyville, Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and there isn't a single mention\Nof the mysterious chest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that came from the\NTree of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor anything about\Nkeys to unlock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But something tells me that\Nopening it is pretty important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Princess\NCelestia has some ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Library in Canterlot\Ndoesn't have anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where\Nelse to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My dearest Twilight, while it\Nwould be perfectly lovely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to have you in\NCanterlot once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another\Noption in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,much closer to Ponyville...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As you know,{\i0}\N{\i1}the ancient Castle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I once shared{\i0}\N{\i1}with Princess Luna{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lies mostly in ruins deep{\i0}\N{\i1}in the Everfree Forest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.27,0:00:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if you look carefully,{\i0}\N{\i1}you may find a book{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that could prove helpful{\i0}\N{\i1}to your research{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hidden somewhere in what's{\i0}\N{\i1}left of the Castle library.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Look at all\Nthese ancient books.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.23,0:01:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a veritable gold\Nmine of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nit! Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.06,0:01:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, heh. So, Twilight.\NUh, ready to head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is PERFECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitles by YayPonies\Nhttp://yayponies.eu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna move.\NYou move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh. There's no way\NI'm moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the most daring\Ndare any pony ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,dare another pony to dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What y'all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash and Applejack are\Ncompeting for the title
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of Most Daring Pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Bee Stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Last pony to blink wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need my bees back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But then we'll never find out\Nwho the Most Daring Pony is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry ladies, I've been\Nkeeping excellent score all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. move the decimal,\Ncarry the two, and ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tied?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be tied for\Nthe Most Daring Pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Numbers don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to stay and\Nkeep keeping score,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but I promised to help\Ntest the new school bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to ring it\Nall week non-stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't even\Nhave to take turns
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because no one\Nelse volunteered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to come up\Nwith another daring dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might have an\Nidea of what we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Rarity, don't you think\Nit's a little late in the day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to be walking through\Nthe forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Star Spider\Nseason, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm sure you have\Na very good reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply the most important reason\NI've ever had in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, then I'm\Nhappy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors that the\NCastle of the Two Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is filled with the most gorgeous\Nof ancient tapestries
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of Pony History.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It pains me to think of those\Nmagnificent creations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,rotting away in those old\Nruins, totally unappreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I require your help in\Nborrowing one or two
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to bring back to the boutique\Nwhere I can restore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll even use the\Npatterns as the inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for a new line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That does sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, maybe not the\Nmost important thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in my entire life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but retro-ancient\Nclassical will be all the rage
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,next season, so it's\Nnothing to sneeze at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you sure you\Nneed those tapestries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, I must admit,\Nthese ruins are a fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the\Ndirt everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's practically an\Nartistic treasure trove
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of ancient good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel, you really shouldn't\Nhave run off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ancient ruins are filled with\Nall sorts of things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that can hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You could stub your toe\Nor trip on a loose stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll need\Nall these candles, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really only\Nscared for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these aren't\Nfor you, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to be studying\Nlate into the night
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're going to need\Nall the light we can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh ? What's so daring\Nabout this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where we got the\NElements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was just a filly,\NGrannie Smith told me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of an ancient legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When Nightmare\NMoon was banished,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,not every last bit of her\Ndark magic went with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grannie used to say when{\i0}\N{\i1}night falls on the Castle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that magic takes the form of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,THE PONY OF SHADOWS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean like a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No pony knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it certainly could\Nuse some restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Be a dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly up there and lift\Nit off that hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe from below?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's so\Ndaring about an old legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I don't\Nbelieve in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You might wanna re-think\Nyour position on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,RUN!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, I think I hurt my wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my dear, I\Nam so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That tapestry is\Nfar too heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to\Nfind a smaller one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, pray tell, did\Nyou disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,While you were struggling\Nunder that fabric,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire wall\Nspun around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have activated\Na secret door.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose these ruins\Nare chock-full of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We must use the\Nutmost care as we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. So maybe the\Nlegend is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's why I\Nbrought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess only the most\Ndaring pony of all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,could stay in this\Ncastle all night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,without\Nbeing scared off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, me neither!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever stays in the Castle the\Nlongest is the Most Daring Pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's gonna take a lot more\Nthan some shadowy ghost pony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to get me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Find anything, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Journal of the\NTwo Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is the book Princess\NCelestia was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope you're not afraid\Nof the dark, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say that I am,\Nbut even if I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be at least fifty percent\Nless scared of it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,than you, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how all\Nthat math works because
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a dark hallway full\Nof disembodied pony legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Nothing\Ncreepy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm starting to wonder{\i0}\N{\i1}if maybe this castle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doesn't want my expertise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, have you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure he made the\Ntrip down with us, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An ancient castle is\Nno place for a bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He could get hit\Nby falling debris
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,or the floor could\Ngive out under him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! He could be trapped in a\Ndark place with no way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine\Nhow that might feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, if you're scared,\Nyou can just admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to put\Nyour hoof around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ALIVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, tapestries or no, I have\Nhad just about enough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,of secret passages,\Nmysterious presences
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and unappreciative castles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not with Angel lost somewhere\Nin this dangerous old Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He could be trapped\Nunder a crumbling statue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,or stuck high in a tower\Nwithout food or water
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,or any friends at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, you've got to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I love to duck behind\Nthe paintings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and though the Hall of Hooves
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,still gives her a\Nbit of a fright,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the trap door slide\Nis Luna's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hall of Hooves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon the Organ to the\NOutside will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the Organ\Nto the Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the creepy sound\Nof a haunted pipe organ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit being such\Na scaredy dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This castle is\Nthousands of years old
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and half of it was destroyed\Nby Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it makes\Nstrange sounds;
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's practically\Nfalling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel? Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They are perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No castle in its right mind\Ncould possibly object
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to my restoring such\Nexquisite works of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're lovely, Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have to keep\Nlooking for Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he doesn't think\NI've given up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't be a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think there's a\Nsingle room in this Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that isn't filled with\Nterrifying things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just old pony armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.06,0:13:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's going\Nto come to life or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you look here, Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are very old and\Nvery scary,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but your wall art is\Nin an atrocious state
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and there is nothing you\Ncan do to keep me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,from my sacred task\Nof restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you went back to\NPonyville, that means I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know hiding isn't really\Nyour sense of humor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but please let this be a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if I don't find you,\NI win by default. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the castles\Nin Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,this is by far the\Nmost ungrateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hope you two\Nare together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Haunted statues, creepy armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Castle, is\Nthat all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to restore\Nancient art!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,ANGEL!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What it the world is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably just more strange\Nsounds of this old castle
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No one likes sarcasm, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What got into them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's OK, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're OK. YOU'RE OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Everypony STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Must.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Save.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you all spent\Nthe whole night
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,running around\Nscaring each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,On what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,On whether or not you're\Nthe Pony of Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the Pony of Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just an\Nold pony's tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who's playing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,THE PONY OF SHADOWS!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know I can\Ntotally play the organ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,PINKIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Pony\Nof Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pony of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,See? What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had to ring\Nthe school bell all week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I only had to ring\Nit for like, five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that was good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then I decided to throw a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished Ringing The\NSchool Bell party,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't have\Nany bluebells
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't throw a Finished\NRinging The School Bell party
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,without bluebells so I went to\NEverfree forest to pick some,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but it started to\Nget so chilly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to wrap myself up in\Nthe tarp I was gonna use
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to gather flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I saw\NFluttershy and Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but they went into the Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,before I could invite\Nthem to my party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I followed\Nthem inside
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so I could help you all\Nwith your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What party is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, The Everypony Come To\NThe Scary Old Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hide From Each Other While\NI Play The Organ Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear this is going right\Nback where I found it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,just as soon as I've returned\Nit to its former glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now don't go running off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. I can't believe I\Nwas so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I let my imagination\Nget the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we all did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I always let my imagination\Nrun away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it comes back with cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's good to know that\Nwhenever your imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is getting away from you, a good\Nfriend can help you rein it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though I didn't\Nfind anything out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,about the mysterious chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was here to\Nhelp all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly did\Nthat, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why weren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Reading Celestia's diary\Nmade it hard to be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,because I knew what it was like\Nwhen she and Luna lived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing something\Nabout the past
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,made it easier to deal with my\Nproblems in the present,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,even the scary ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought of a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we keep a journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the Royal\NPony Sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! That way we can\Nlearn from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe someday other\Nponies will read it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and learn something too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What a splendid idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what my\Nfirst entry will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Diary, I'm glad Grannie\NSmith's legend wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Me three, because\Nthat means you two
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,are still tied for\NMost Daring Pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Shadow ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How ridiculous is that?
